## ShellSpec Configuration

## Default shell
--shell zsh

## Helper file (loaded before each spec)
--require spec_helper

## Shell options (exported to test environment)
--env GOODMORNING_NO_AUTO_RUN=1
--env GOODMORNING_SHOW_SETUP_MESSAGES=false

## Output format
--format documentation

## Exclude real API tests by default (run with: shellspec --tag real)
--tag ~real

## Fail fast (stop on first failure)
# --fail-fast

## Random execution order
# --random

## Coverage (requires kcov)
# --kcov

## Parallel execution (faster test runs)
# --jobs 4
